      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3045-3083",
      "markText": "《欲乐园》希望人们思考的是：在当今社会中，人应该怎样生活，才算是真的生存过。",
      "totalCount": 495,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=32765481&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3045&rangeEnd=3083",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ded3238071f3f629ded3cbe?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3045&rangeEnd=3083"
    },
    {
